Best Of Vocal Trance Classics (2013) 

                          Trance | Amsterdam Trance 

            320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-10-07 | 02:34:40 | 362 Mb


Amsterdam Trance Radio connects with Amsterdam Trance Records to reveal some of the finest moment of the trance genre with a selection of The Best of Vocal Trance Classics! Outstanding tracks from such Artists as Armin van Buuren, Andain, First State, Myon & Shane, Susana, Glenn Morrison, Christian Burns, Dark matters, The Doppler Effect, Richard Durand, Neev Kennedy, Elles de Graaf, Anita Kelsey and the never previously released 2013 Remastering of Ferry Corstens Pulp Victim Classic "The World".
